# Prettier ignores for repo-root runs.
# The frontend has its own .prettierrc + .prettierignore and is checked separately in CI.

# Dependencies & build output
**/node_modules
**/.next
**/target

# Lockfiles
**/pnpm-lock.yaml

# Binary assets
**/*.png
**/*.webp
**/*.gif
**/*.ico

# Private, secret-containing docs (also gitignored) and generated HTML
docs/disscount_*
docs/*.html
